md:
giải nghĩa từ "foliage" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ trái nghĩa.

* Foliage (noun)
	+ Meaning: The leaves of a plant or tree, especially when they are considered as a whole.
	+ Vietnamese: Lá cây, lá xanh
	+ Example sentence: The foliage of the tree was a vibrant green.
	+ Related words: leaf, greenery, vegetation
	+ Antonyms: bareness, barrenness

* Foliage (noun)
	+ Meaning: The arrangement of leaves on a stem or branch.
	+ Vietnamese: Cách sắp xếp lá trên thân hoặc nhánh
	+ Example sentence: The foliage of the orchid was delicate and intricate.
	+ Related words: leaf arrangement, leaf pattern
	+ Antonyms: disarrangement, disorder

* Foliage (noun)
	+ Meaning: A decorative design or pattern featuring leaves.
	+ Vietnamese: Thiết kế trang trí hoặc hoa văn lá
	+ Example sentence: The wallpaper had a beautiful foliage design.
	+ Related words: leaf pattern, floral design
	+ Antonyms: plain design, simple pattern
